  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[970ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1715248811735-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1715248811735-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1715248811735-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1715248811735-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1715248811735-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel lengths off your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p><p>Roll your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a colander and rinse under <strong>cold running water</strong> to refresh them</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1715248815603-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1715248815603-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1715248815603-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1715248815603-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1715248815603-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>courgette ribbons</strong> and <strong>refreshed peas</strong> to a bowl with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>courgette & pea salad</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Set aside half the refreshed peas and leave plain!</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1715248819814-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
