          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1715248819814-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>sliced prosciutto</strong> to a plate and put in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 4-5 min, then set aside until serving to dry and crisp up – this is your <strong>crispy prosciutto</strong></p><p>Tip: Check your sliced prosciutto every 30 secs to prevent it from burning, as microwave temperatures vary!</p>",
