    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
