    {
      "instruction": "<p>Break the <strong>crispy prosciutto</strong> into shards and serve the <strong>cheesy risotto</strong> topped with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, <strong>prosciutto shards</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>truffle oil</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave the truffle oil or just add a little!</span></strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>courgette & pea salad </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>to the side</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Serve the peas to the side</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
